Maintainer: Josh Betz <jbetz@jhu.edu>
Description: This package provides relatively ready-to-analyze data from 
  randomized controlled trials for use in teaching and software development.
  All data is retrieved from other sources and processed to make it ready to
  use, including variable labels and data dictionaries.
